com.barryholroyd.lib

Class Separators

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.barryholroyd.lib.Separators

  • public class Separators
extends java.lang.Object
    Create text separators of various sorts. Different levels have different characters and string lengths (decreasing levels have decreasing prominence).
    • separators are one-liners.
    • headers are three-liners.
    Externally, use '#' for the highest level separator.

    Internally, the levels are as follows.

    1. *
    2. =
    3. -
